                        <interp inst="t18470614-name-1074" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HARVEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant R</hi> 4.) This watch was found on the prisoner, and brought to the station by a constable who was dismissed the next day—the prisoner said he took the watch from the water-closet, and that was not stealing.</p>
